title: Nenjukulle Nee Minnaladippa Lyrics
stanzas:
Song: Nenjukulle Nee Minnaladippa
Singer(s): Vijay Prakash, Diwakar, Ajeesh Ashok
Movie: Vadacurry
Music: Vivek Shiva and Mervin Solomo
Lyrics: Ponraj

Nenjukulle Nee Minnaladippa
kannukulla nee kadha padippa.
gundu kuli un, srippaala
piththu pidikkum nenachaala.

Ava paathaale paththikkumey
sirichaale sikkikkumey
uyir meley keley vandhu oonjal aadudhadi.

un Pinnaale nikkum koottam
thannaale  podum aattam
kondaada neeyum vandhaa semma sandhosam.

Kandapadi kandapadi, kolluddhadi kalla vizhi
vandhu enna yethukkadi nee. (2)

Thagaraare illaama, thalli nikkureney mayangaama
thayangaama konjam thaadi arakirukkaa naan aanendi

Ada yaarodu yaarannnu eludhivittaan anga
unnodu naannu solli vacheney.
Un alavaana azhagaala pasi thookkam pochu
marukkaama verukkaama yethukkodi.

Engirundho vandha azhage
unna enni enni naanum parakka.
Ini ulagazhi ingae vandhaalum
avala oora vittu oda solluven.

Kandapadi kandapadi, kolluddhadi kalla vizhi
vandhu enna yethukkadi nee. (2)
